description: Since it's getting close to halloween I thought I would pull out the Ouija board and see if I could contact some spirits. Specifically, the spirit of the late Ben Hurst, a legendary director who worked on Sonic Underground. Things got a little out of hand and honestly, I cannot believe I got this on camera! It's definitely not something you be able to believe unless you saw it for yourself.
